---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About EV Auto Pro | China NEV Export Specialist Since 2010"
  description="15+ years in China export trade. Authorized exporter of Changan, Deepal, Jetour, Geely, Volkswagen, BYD. Founder-led, 60+ countries served."
>
  <section class="bg-ink-50 border-b border-ink-200 py-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="text-xs text-ink-500 mb-3"><a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-500">Home</a> · <span class="text-ink-900">About</span></nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink-900">About EV Auto Pro</h1>
      <p class="text-base text-ink-600 mt-2 max-w-2xl">
        Authorized China new energy vehicle exporter. Founder-led. Russian / Arabic / Spanish ops. 60+ countries served.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-ink">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink-900 mb-4">15 Years Building Trust</h2>
      <p class="text-base text-ink-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        EV Auto Pro was founded by <strong>Cai</strong>, a 15-year veteran of Chinese export trade. From 2010 to 2022, we served as a multi-category sourcing agent for international wholesale buyers across textiles, home decor, and machinery. In 2022, we pivoted exclusively to <strong>new energy vehicles</strong> in response to the global surge in demand for affordable Chinese EVs, PHEVs, and hybrids.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-ink-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Today we hold direct authorized-dealer MoUs with <strong>Changan, Deepal, Qiyuan, Geely, Volkswagen (China), and Jetour</strong>, with active sourcing relationships across 35 additional Chinese OEMs.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink-900 mb-4 mt-12">What Sets Us Apart</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-base text-ink-700">
        <li><strong>Founder-led negotiation</strong> — no layered middlemen, direct quote within 24 hours</li>
        <li><strong>Native Russian & CIS specialization</strong> — EAC certification process handled in-house</li>
        <li><strong>Transparent pricing</strong> — FOB / CIF / EXW broken down line-by-line, no hidden fees</li>
        <li><strong>Bonded warehouse stock</strong> — 200+ units ready to ship from Shanghai</li>
        <li><strong>After-sales parts depots</strong> — Moscow, Almaty, Dubai for fast spare delivery</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink-900 mb-4 mt-12">Compliance & Certifications</h2>
      <p class="text-base text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
        We hold full MoFCOM Export License, AEO Customs certification, and ISO 9001. For destination compliance we navigate GCC (UAE/Saudi), EAC (Russia/CIS), INMETRO (Brazil), and SASO/GSO (Saudi) requirements as part of every shipment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-ink-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Talk to our export team</h2>
      <p class="text-base text-ink-300 mb-6">Get FOB + CIF pricing for your target market within 24 hours.</p>
      <a href="/contact/quote/" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
